headline: KLA Declares Regular Cash Dividend
summary: The KLA Corporation (NASDAQ: KLAC) Board of Directors today declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.70 per share on its common stock, payable on March 4, 2025 to KLA shareholders of record as of the close of business on Feb. 24, 2025.
